description: The bog is more water than land here, the dark pools stained a rich brown with tannins from the forest.  Long strands of moss drape curtainlike from branches stretched out over a pile of logs that form a crude bridge.  An owl hoots from its hidden perch.

The bog is more water than land here, the dark pools stained a rich brown with tannins from the forest.  Long strands of moss drape curtainlike from branches stretched out over a pile of logs that form a crude bridge.  A bright green-throated duck gives a raucous call, then splashes off into the dank interior.
title: [Emerald Forest, Peat Bog]
